1. Moving the sun with ctrl+L+mouse doesn't work, set the sky sphere and set its directional light actor to none. Then you can modify the overrides manually. See
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lRUAk6AxjHU

2. **** Shadows not changing with sun, select direction light and ROTATE it around so the shadows will change direction. It appears the sun sky sphere operates
independent from the directional light in some projects
https://answers.unrealengine.com/questions/127324/sun-direction-not-updating.html

